description:
The Free Planets Alliance battleship Tlahuixcalpantecuhtli was the flagship of the Free Planets Alliance`s 9th Fleet, under the command of Vice Admiral Vittorio di Bertini. Pennant number 0901.
Tlahuixcalpantecuhtli is the Aztec "Lord of Dawn," or the god of Venus, the morning star. In Aztec mythology, Tlahuixcalpantecuhtli was believed to be a dangerous and malevolent entity, closely associated with the god Quetzacoatl.
